  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0d9c\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Polonnaruwa farmers are in trouble as paddy prices have dropped",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena said today (23) in Polonnaruwa that the farmer is in a serious crisis due to the decrease in the price of paddy.",
        "Also, he said that the development projects started in Polonnaruwa when he was the president were in ruins and he spoke strongly to the parliament, the government and the media and it was not his fault.",
        "According to this, the administrative building complex built in Polonnaruwa is currently growing wild and the former president made these comments when he met journalists in Polonnaruwa to urgently inform about it.",
        "\"The people of Polonnaruwa know that I have done a huge amount of work. I am not going to tell each other. It is now August, but the lakes in Polonnaruwa are full and all the canals are flowing. This has happened because the Moragaha Kanda Kalu Gaga reservoirs were built. I am now everywhere in the villages of the district yesterday. Yesterday, a serious issue has arisen especially regarding the decrease in the price of paddy.",
        "The farmers of the Batticaloa district came and met me yesterday, representatives of the farmers' organizations. They say that as soon as one acre is cultivated, one lakh rupees will be lost. Now everywhere in Polonnaruwa, the farmers are saying that they are losing so much from paddy. Therefore, the farmer is in serious trouble.",
        "The government should focus on this, the Ministry of Agriculture should focus on this, the Ministry of Finance should focus on this and give relief to the farmers, otherwise the farmers will not do farming."
      ],
